The paper discusses the development of an intelligent and adaptive e-learning system that uses expert systems to determine the learning style and characteristics of the learner, plan pre-tests, and evaluate post-tests. This involves the integration of adaptive web-based e-learning with expert systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.ED (Education), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
